FBIS3-27980 "dreas022_i_94002" FBIS-EAS-94-022 Document Type:Daily Report 2 Feb 1994 SOUTHEAST ASIA Cambodia VGNUFC: Chea Sim Opposes National Reconciliation BK0202022094 (Clandestine) Voice of the Great National Union Front of Cambodia in Cambodian 2330 GMT 1 Feb 94 BK0202022094 (Clandestine) Voice of the Great National Union Front of Cambodia Language: Cambodian Article Type:BFN [Excerpt] During a meeting with the Canadian envoy in Phnom Penh on 29 January, the puppet Chea Sim declared his vehement opposition to national reconciliation. He demanded that Democratic Kampuchea implement his three conditions before any other issue is discussed. This declaration clearly proves that the Vietnamese communist puppets -- on orders from their bosses -- do not accept His Majesty King Norodom Sihanouk's five-point political plan to secure national reconciliation and genuine peace in Cambodia. [passage omitted]
